{"tid":1778072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局表示：6月中起有30宗投訴成立 老師或被取消註冊","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:33:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd3585f9bd5200e6ba3e735874b88f062a31ae4","tid":1778072,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"教育局稱30宗涉老師操守調查初步成立　正考慮懲處<br />\n<br />\n一名教師昨日被捕，教育局表示，已要求學校履行作為僱主以及確保學生安全的責任，考慮暫停該教師的職務。教育局表示，十分重視教師的專業操守及學生的行為，指教師的言行須符合社會的道德及專業方面的期望，局方會嚴肅跟進每個被判罪、被捕及被投訴的老師個案。 發言人說，自6月中至上月初，教育局已就106宗與近期社會事件有關的教師專業操守個案展開調查，目前已初步完成60宗個案，包括早前已發出譴責信的兩宗個案，當中約30宗初步成立，教育局正考慮應作出的懲處。至於被捕教師的數目，發言人說，由於涉及法律程序，局方現階段不便置評，但教育局會根據《教育條例》嚴肅跟進違法的教師，如果情況嚴重，可以取消註冊。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-10 22:37:30<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497021-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497021-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=39ac1a11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497021-20191210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f0f1757d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497021-20191210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f8d6fff3bf8f15cebc3ee8cedb3bc9e9ab4dfa17","tid":1778072,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46d4ab6143c907e9976d910165bcec76a1a96ff0","tid":1778072,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/appbKX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FappbKX7.png&h=8f2f454d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"